        "id": 5255
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-07-19T14:41:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This block should happen inside onStartIncrementalDecode. That is how we start an incremental decode. Calls to onIncrementalDecode continue it. So we don\u0027t want to redo setup.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 790,
        "startChar": 7,
